  "text": "## Complaints & Support  \n**Q: What if I'm unhappy with my service?**\nA: Contact us:\n- **Phone:** 0800-555-2265 (Mon–Fri 08:00–20:00, Sat 09:00–17:00)\n- **Email:** support@firstuk.bank\n- **Branch:** Visit any FirstUK branch\n- **Online:** Submit complaint form at www.firstuk.bank  \n**Q: What if I'm not satisfied with FirstUK Bank's response?**\nA: You can escalate to:\n- **Financial Ombudsman Service (FOS)**\n- Phone: 0800 023 4567\n- Website: www.financialombudsman.org.uk\n- Free and independent  \n**Q: How long does FirstUK take to respond to complaints?**\nA:\n- Standard: Within 8 calendar days\n- Complex issues: Up to 8 weeks (we'll explain why)  \n---",
